statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from "tram_documento" inner join "tram_operacion" as "o" on "iddocumento" = "o"."oper_iddocumento" inner join "tram_tipodocumento" as "td" on "docu_idtipodocumento" = "td"."idtdoc" left join "tram_dependencia" as "depe" on "o"."oper_iddependencia" = "depe"."iddependencia" left join "tram_dependencia" as "ddoc" on "o"."oper_depeid_d" = "ddoc"."iddependencia" left join "tram_dependencia" as "ddest" on "docu_iddependencia" = "ddest"."iddependencia" left join "admin" as "u1" on "o"."oper_usuid_d" = "u1"."id" where ("o"."oper_procesado" = 0 and "o"."oper_iddependencia" = 2 and "o"."oper_idusuario" = '2') and ("o"."oper_idtope" = 1 or "o"."oper_idtope" = 2)

select "o"."idoperacion", "iddocumento", "docu_idexma", "docu_origen", "docu_fecha_doc", "o"."oper_forma", "o"."oper_acciones", "o"."oper_detalledestino", "docu_folios", "td"."tdoc_descripcion", "docu_numero_doc", "docu_siglas_doc", "docu_firma", "docu_cargo", "docu_asunto", "docu_iddependencia" as "depe_origen", "ddest"."depe_nombre" as "depe_nombre_origen", "o"."oper_idtope", "o"."oper_depeid_d" as "depe_destino", "ddoc"."depe_nombre" as "depe_nombre_destino", "o"."oper_usuid_d", "docu_idtipodocumento", "u1"."adm_name" as "nameuser_destino", "u1"."adm_lastname" as "lastnameuser_destino", "docu_idusuario", "o"."oper_idusuario", "u1"."adm_estado", "docu_doc_generado", "docu_firma_electronica", "docu_digital", "depe"."depe_recibetramite", "o"."created_at" from "tram_documento" inner join "tram_operacion" as "o" on "iddocumento" = "o"."oper_iddocumento" inner join "tram_tipodocumento" as "td" on "docu_idtipodocumento" = "td"."idtdoc" left join "tram_dependencia" as "depe" on "o"."oper_iddependencia" = "depe"."iddependencia" left join "tram_dependencia" as "ddoc" on "o"."oper_depeid_d" = "ddoc"."iddependencia" left join "tram_dependencia" as "ddest" on "docu_iddependencia" = "ddest"."iddependencia" left join "admin" as "u1" on "o"."oper_usuid_d" = "u1"."id" where ("o"."oper_procesado" = 0 and "o"."oper_iddependencia" = 2 and "o"."oper_idusuario" = '2') and ("o"."oper_idtope" = 1 or "o"."oper_idtope" = 2) order by "o"."idoperacion" desc limit 10 offset 0
